metadata.description:
A generative token of gratitude.

Controls:
1) The keys from '1' to '9' can be used to re-render the artwork, where the number corresponds to the resolution multiplier (e.g., press '4' to render at 4x the initial resolution);
2) 'S' to save;
3) 'B' to toggle the blur effect on/off (this will re-render your artwork).

Features:
1) Hue: 12 Variations;
2) Number of Flowers: 5 | 15 | 25;
3) Colour of the Flower: White & Yellow | Monochromatic | Random;
4) Size of the Flower: Big | Medium | Small;
5) Distance from the Center: Big | Medium | Small;

Made with Vanilla JS
